{{Quote|The Great Well! Source of all life on our planet, birthground of our serpent steeds, and the place where you will be judged by our Supreme Master!|[[Varn (individual)|Varn]] to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]|<ref name="serpent" />}}
The '''Great Well''' was a large sinkhole on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ophideraan]] that contained the main source of [[Water/Legends|water]] on the arid world, and contained the [[Cavern of the Serpents|breeding ground]] for the distinctive [[flying serpent]] [[Species/Legends|species]] that dominated Ophideraan's skies. The [[Serpent Masters]], a group of scavengers who ruled over the planet during the era of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], lived in a facility built within the Great Well. The Serpent Masters' [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]] lived deeper within the Great Well, where they spent their days maintaining the pumping systems built into the water source.<ref name="serpent" />

